Package: gitty
Version: 2.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: git, libc6
Recommends: gh, xclip | xsel | wl-clipboard
Maintainer: Omibranch <omibranch@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Minimal Git CLI wrapper that speaks human
 gitty wraps common git operations into short, readable commands.
 Supports push/pull with conflict resolution, checkpoints, branch
 management, repo stats, and interactive .gitignore picker.
Homepage: https://github.com/Omibranch/gitty
